		<div id=intro>
			This is the software package repository for the domain <b>%domain%</b>.
			</p>
			Linux workstations and servers in this domain should be configured to use this as their software repository. It is a
			mirror of archive.ubuntu.com that adds additional software and removes software that is against domain policy.
			</p>
			To use this repository, the /etc/apt/sources.list configuration file should use <b>%repoServerName%</b> as the domain for
			all sources instead of <i>*archive.ubuntu.com</i>
